DataElement.preferredName: External Publication To Study Protocol Reference Publication Identifier ISO21090.II.v1.0
DataElement.preferredDefinition: A unique symbol that establishes identity of a publication related to the study protocol background. EXAMPLE(S): 10987815 is the unique PubMed Identifier (PMID) for the citation in MEDLINE.
